    dc:description "Figure 11. Amara (Curtonotus) macronota A dorsal habitus, male (Gujiao, Shanxi) B pronotum posterior angle C male mesotibia D lateral view of aedeagus E right paramere F apical lamella G female gonocoxite (Shunyi, Beijing). Scale bars: 5 mm (A); 1 mm (B-E); 0.5 mm (F, G)." ;
